## AI Data Flow (How It Works)

```
User submits content
    ↓
Node.js /analyze route
    ↓  POST
Python /ai/analyze  ←→  Gemini / OpenRouter LLM
    ↓
Returns: { findings, root_cause, predictions, fix_suggestions, 
           anomalies, risk_score, confidence, summary }
    ↓
Node.js blends with regex line numbers (secondary)
    ↓
Also calls: /ai/predict (predictions) + /ai/correlate (correlation)
    ↓
Frontend renders: Insights + Predictions + Dashboard + Chat
```

