## ⚠️ Action Required: API Key

The existing API keys in `ai-service/.env` are **expired/invalid**. The platform runs in graceful fallback mode (regex only, no AI reasoning), which is why you may see *"AI reasoning unavailable"*.

**To activate full AI reasoning, do ONE of the following:**

### Option A — Get a free Gemini key (recommended)
1. Go to **https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey**
2. Create a new API key
3. Open `ai-service/.env`, set:
   ```
   LLM_BACKEND=gemini
   GEMINI_API_KEY=<your-new-key>
   ```
4. Restart the AI service

### Option B — Get a free OpenRouter key  
1. Go to **https://openrouter.ai** → Sign Up → API Keys
2. Create a free key (they give $5 free credit)
3. Open `ai-service/.env`, set:
   ```
   LLM_BACKEND=openrouter
   OPENROUTER_API_KEY=<your-new-key>
   OPENROUTER_MODEL=google/gemma-3-27b-it:free
   ```
4. Restart the AI service: run `.\venv\Scripts\python.exe app.py` in `ai-service/`

